HEADWORD: Authoress
<hw>Au"thor*ess</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A female author.</def>
<rj><au>Glover.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><note>⟦hand⟧ The word is not very much used, <xex>author</xex> being
commonly applied to a female writer as well as to a male.</note>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Authorial</ent>⟦br⟧
